whether you touch them or not.

326
00:16:55.056 --> 00:16:56.367
MAN: Oh. wow.

327
00:16:56.391 --> 00:16:57.993
Well. that's good to know.

328
00:16:58.017 --> 00:17:00.371
Like anyone can tell
the fucking difference.

329
00:17:00.395 --> 00:17:01.956
