343
00:17:41.686 --> 00:17:42.729
NIKI: Yeah.

344
00:17:43.605 --> 00:17:44.773
(WOMAN SIGHS)

345
00:17:47.692 --> 00:17:49.253
NIKI: (SIGHS) God damn it.

346
00:17:49.277 --> 00:17:51.404
